  ("npc2_backstory_response_2", "Hard luck, friend. Good day to you, and stay away from the sea."), #Aleifr
  ("npc3_backstory_response_2", "Go back to your master, lass. Forget your old life and accept your destiny as a slave for good."), #Eithne
  ("npc4_backstory_response_2", "No, sorry, I haven't heard of one."), #Athrwys ap Gwawrddur
  ("npc5_backstory_response_2", "Sigh... So long as the noble clans fight family against family, these lands will never have true peace."), #Frioc
  ("npc6_backstory_response_2", "Away with you, accursed fratricide!"), #Bodero
  ("npc7_backstory_response_2", "Actually, I'm rather fond of the place. And, no, I have not perceived anything. Good day to you."), #Bridei
