  ("npc9_backstory_response_2", "Some of my best friends are riff-raff. Good day to you, sir."), #Lothar
  ("npc10_backstory_response_2", "No doubt you'll eventually find your Saxon King. Or, maybe, a Briton will kill you. Good day."), #Ceawlin
  ("npc11_backstory_response_2", "Very interesting, milady, but I have work to do, and no time to chat about your miserable love life."), #Gwenllian
