  ("npc1_signup", "{Sir/Madame} -- I'm offended that you would even think such a thing. I'd be most indebted to you if you let me join your shield-wall, and I can completely assure that my eyes are the ones of a lynx. Only weak-minded men lose their sight because of simple, innocent drinks..."), #Osmund
  ("npc2_signup", "Well, I will confess that I am not a warrior by trade, even though war runs through the blood of my people."), #Aleifr
  ("npc3_signup", "Do you? Really, would you help me escape and protect me? Well, I am in no position to be picky! I would be pleased to join you in exchange for my freedom."), #Eithne
  ("npc4_signup", "Good! I look forward to vanquishing your enemies and to finding my long lost father."), #Athrwys ap Gwawrddur
  ("npc5_signup", "Why, that is a most generous offer."), #Frioc
  ("npc6_signup", "Yes! You must have been sent by divine providence! Lead me -- lead me away from darkness into the battlefield!"), #Bodero
  ("npc7_signup", "I might be. I could certainly use the money."), #Bridei
  ("npc8_signup", "Can you? I shall accept your offer. But, believe me, I will outshine every warrior under your command. Are you prepared to have such a mighty warrior as myself in your shield-wall?"), #Siwi
  ("npc9_signup", "I would very much like that, {sir/madame}"), #Lothar
  ("npc10_signup", "Well, I guess I can give you the chance to prove your worthiness. I shall fight for you."), #Ceawlin
  ("npc11_signup", "Why, maybe I could join you? Well, you seem a very fine future for me... I mean, working for you {handsome/beauty}..."), #Gwenllian
  ("npc12_signup", "As I told you, I am a leech, not some silk-robed forum physician who has never touched a body. I can get my hands dirty."), #Orosio
  ("npc13_signup", "I would be pleased to ride with you, at least for a little while, for pay and a share of any loot."), #Liuva
  ("npc14_signup", "Indeed? You would do well to enlist me."), #Brian
  ("npc15_signup", "Creta, eventually, but I'd welcome the opportunity to get a few scillingas in my pocket, first, so I don't arrive home empty-handed. So if you promise me food and a share of the loot, I'd be happy to fight with you for a while."), #Agasicles
  ("npc16_signup", "Well, {sir/madame}, let me tell you. Even though my main mission is spiritual, and I shall bring peace to every soul in this shield-wall, I can also fight and battle alongside your men, since God does not avert violence for a just and Christian cause."), #Aedh
  ("npc_bashe_signup", "Thank you. My fate seemed uncertain, but you have given me a goal. I will be your bodyguard. An elite warrior fighting only by your side."),
  ("npc_sange_signup", "Thank you. My fate seemed uncertain, but you have given me a goal. I will be your bodyguard. An elite warrior fighting only by your side."),
  ("npc_paintrain_signup", "Thank you. My fate seemed uncertain, but you have given me a goal. I will be your bodyguard. An elite warrior fighting only by your side."),
  ("npc_hammertime_signup", "Thank you. My fate seemed uncertain, but you have given me a goal. I will be your bodyguard. An elite warrior fighting only by your side."),
  ("npc_tank_signup", "I have a proper education, and many years of experience."),
  ("npc_backwoodsharry_signup", "I come from Frisia. Frisian women are strong and beautiful."),
  ("npc_deadeye_signup", "Very well, Drythen.  My father once told me, 'The fates will often send aid unlooked for, if one is worthy'. Perhaps...  Well, leave it for now."),
  ("npc_probulator_signup", "I am a capable ruler, and can effectively order the populace."),
  ("npc_grim_signup", "Tavernkeep! Bring me another cup of mead!"),
  ("npc_enchantress_signup", "I have many years of experience."),

  ("npc1_signup_2", "I've ridden over a fair amount of rough country in my time, more often than not in a hurry. I'm a good tracker and I've got a good eye for terrain, mead, and beer. So what do you say?"), #Osmund
  ("npc2_signup_2", "I'm a fast learner. I can ride, and know a fair bit about trade, prices, and such."), #Aleifr
  ("npc3_signup_2", "I think you would find that I would be a most valuable addition to your ranks. I am well-versed in the old traditions of the land and can declaim several of the epic poems of my people. I play the harp and am a skilled manager of household servants. I will also use everything my grandma taught me to keep my new companions healthy."), #Eithne
  ("npc4_signup_2", "Note however that as a gentleman and of righteous noble birth, I expect to be in a position of command, and not be treated as one of the common soldiers."), #Athrwys ap Gwawrddur
  ("npc5_signup_2", "I shall not betray you -- so long, of course, as you do your duty to me by feeding me, paying me, and not dragging my miserable hide into a battle where there is no chance of winning. Vow to respect me, and I shall be your best warrior."), #Frioc
  ("npc6_signup_2", "I am well-practiced in the arts of war -- but I beg you, {sir/madame}, I wish to use my skills to defend the innocent, the pure, and to kill Visigoths -- as many as possible --, not to be a common brigand and wreak more misery than I have already wrought."), #Bodero
  ("npc7_signup_2", "But let your followers know that I do not suffer louts and brutes. Anyone who misbehaves around me will quickly find an arrow in their gullet."), #Bridei
  ("npc8_signup_2", "I shall be pleased to fight in your shield-wall. But I warn you -- if you ask me to gather the firewood, or cook a meal, you will not like the consequences."), #Siwi
  ("npc9_signup_2", "I am a gentleman, and I prefer to fight with sword and lance. I recognize that you are of lower birth than I am, but there is no shame for me to serve under an experienced warlord -- presuming, of course, that your followers do not become too familiar with me, nor too jealous of my bravery. I assume that will not be a problem?"), #Lothar
  ("npc10_signup_2", "You won't regret taking me on, {sir/milady}. I'm a very experienced warrior, deadly against those damn Britons. And I've trained more raw recruits than you've had hot dinners, begging your pardon."), #Ceawlin
  ("npc11_signup_2", "I know how to swing a blade because I had to defend myself at home, staunch a wound, because that old fart loved to fight in taverns, and to feed men, because, well, the pig used to eat like a bear. It would be a foolish warlord who passed up the opportunity to hire someone as experienced as me! Say, {handsome/beauty}, don't you command a shield-wall of your own, now?"), #Gwenllian
  ("npc12_signup_2", "I have treated every variety of wound that can be inflicted by the hand of man. Before I was a leech, I was a hot-tempered student, so you may be sure that I have inflicted wounds as well as healed them."), #Orosio
  ("npc13_signup_2", "I am a skilled swordsman, and I can also instruct your men in fighting. But I warn you that I do not care to fight for a leader who is lax in discipline with {his/her} men, for in the long run they will not respect a soft hand. "), #Liuva
  ("npc14_signup_2", "Sword, lance, the bow -- my skill in all such martial pursuits is the stuff of epic verse.  Together we will perform feats that will be recounted in festivals and campfires, in filthy taverns and in the halls of kings, for many generations to come."), #Brian
  ("npc15_signup_2", "Siege work is my specialty, although I reckon can handle myself well enough in an open battle, if need be. The fortresses here do not compare to the ones in my homeland, and I can truly help you take any castle you might want in Britannia or Hibernia."), #Agasicles
  ("npc16_signup_2", "I will be useful in every kind of battle, be it mundane, be it spiritual -- be it even against the very hordes of Hell."), #Aedh
  ("npc_bashe_signup_2", "You have just gladdened my day, you could not have found a more faithful bodyguard."),
  ("npc_sange_signup_2", "You have just gladdened my day, you could not have found a more faithful bodyguard."),
  ("npc_paintrain_signup_2", "Allow me time to gather my few possessions and I'll join you outside."),
  ("npc_hammertime_signup_2", "Allow me time to gather my few possessions and I'll join you outside."),
  ("npc_tank_signup_2", "Allow me time to gather my few possessions and I'll join you outside."),
