  ("npc2_signup_response_1", "That will do."), #Aleifr
  ("npc3_signup_response_1", "Hum, that's a start. We can teach you the rest. Hurry, I am rescuing you right now."), #Eithne
  ("npc4_signup_response_1", "Very well. I'll be glad to have you with us, son of Gwawrddur."), #Athrwys ap Gwawrddur
  ("npc5_signup_response_1", "Certainly. Those are my obligations to every man under my command."), #Frioc
  ("npc6_signup_response_1", "Happy to be of service! Get your things together, and we shall be on our way."), #Bodero
  ("npc7_signup_response_1", "I will hire you. Try not to shoot anyone on your first day, though."), #Bridei
