  ("npc10_signup_response_1", "Good man. But, beware, you should respect any Briton or Mercian in our shield-wall."), #Ceawlin
  ("npc11_signup_response_1", "It sounds like you'll be useful. You are hired. But stop calling me '{handsome/beauty}'. Please."), #Gwenllian
  ("npc12_signup_response_1", "Then welcome to our shield-wall, philosopher of nature."), #Orosio
  ("npc13_signup_response_1", "Good. I'll be happy to hire someone like you. I hope you can really turn our Brythonic boys into soldiers."), #Liuva
  ("npc14_signup_response_1", "Good. Make yourself ready, and we'll be on our way. "), #Brian
