  ("npc3_signup_response_2", "Actually, I think you are pretty useless. Go back to your butcher, slave."), #Eithne
  ("npc4_signup_response_2", "Actually, we are not in the habit of hiring men who might have other quests than war in mind. Good day, sir."), #Athrwys ap Gwawrddur
  ("npc5_signup_response_2", "Actually, on second thought, I prefer not to hire a banished man."), #Frioc
  ("npc6_signup_response_2", "On second thought, maybe a shield-wall is not what you need right now."), #Bodero
  ("npc7_signup_response_2", "Actually, on second thought, you sound like you might be trouble. Good day to you. "), #Bridei
  ("npc8_signup_response_2", "Ah. Actually, if you don't do whatever I order you to do, you'd best seek your fortune elsewhere."), #Siwi
  ("npc9_signup_response_2", "You assume wrong, sir. In my shield-wall we respect courage and skill, rather than noble birth. And simple worlds make no man a true brave warrior."), #Lothar  
  ("npc10_signup_response_2", "On second thought, I do not want to see any of my men killed during the night because they are not of Saxon origin. Good day to you."), #Ceawlin
  ("npc11_signup_response_2", "Sorry, milady. We've already got as many in our shield-wall as we can handle. Maybe you should start looking for your future elsewhere."), #Gwenllian
  ("npc12_signup_response_2", "A battle is not the same thing as a tavern brawl. Perhaps you should look elsewhere for work."), #Orosio
  ("npc13_signup_response_2", "Actually, I have no wish to provoke a mutiny in my ranks. My warriors are already disciplined enough. Good day, sir."), #Liuva
  ("npc14_signup_response_2", "Actually, on second thought, a fighter overeager for glory and women is dangerous to have in one's shield-wall."), #Brian
  ("npc15_signup_response_2", "Actually, I need a different kind of expertise. My apologies."), #Agasicles
  ("npc16_signup_response_2", "To be honest, I'd prefer someone who was not a religious fanatic."), #Aedh
  ("npc_bashe_signup_response_2", "Retract your offer and leave."),
  ("npc_sange_signup_response_2", "Retract your offer and leave."),
  ("npc_paintrain_signup_response_2", "I don't need your help."),
  ("npc_hammertime_signup_response_2", "I'll be fine without you."),
  ("npc_tank_signup_response_2", "I'll be fine without you."),
  ("npc_backwoodsharry_signup_response_2", "I'll be fine without you."),
  ("npc_deadeye_signup_response_2", "Truth to tell, I don't think now is the time.  Perhaps later.  Farewell."),
  ("npc_probulator_signup_response_2", "I'll be fine without you."),
  ("npc_grim_signup_response_2", "We have no need of spearmen and skirmishers. Farewell."),
