  ("npc1_payment", "I will be very useful to you, {sir/madame}, you can bet on that. Just one more thing before we leave, would you mind lending me {reg3} scillingas? I am ashamed to say it, but I have made myself a bit of debt here, staying in this tavern over the last few weeks and the tavern owners no longer believe that I am loaded with gold as I used to tell them. You know, things could get ugly here if they see me leaving with you before paying them."), #Osmund
  ("npc2_payment", "Before I sign up, I will need 300 coins here."), #Aleifr
  ("npc3_payment", "Before I sign up, I will need 300 coins here."), #Eithne
  ("npc4_payment", "Excellent. Before we depart, would you be so kind as to lend me {reg3} scillingas? I had to pawn a family heirloom at a pawnbroker here in {s20}, and I would like to retrieve it before we leave."), #Athrwys ap Gwawrddur
  ("npc5_payment", "Thank you. Now, to seal off our agreement, I ask for {reg3} scillingas from you, so I can adequately equip myself with armor and weapons necessary to fill my new obligations to you."), #Frioc
  ("npc6_payment", "Before I sign up, i need pay 300 coins here."), #Bodero
  ("npc7_payment", "All right then. I will come with you. But I want a payment of {reg3} scillingas first. You aren't expecting me to work for free, are you?"), #Bridei
  ("npc8_payment", "Then I will fight your enemies for you. But first I want a bounty of {reg3} scillingas. If you are a worthy warlord who can lead {his/her} shield-wall to riches and plunder, you should have no trouble paying. I cannot afford to follow a pauper."), #Siwi
  ("npc9_payment", "That's very good of you. And before I join, can you lend me {reg3} scillingas, so that I can buy some proper clothing that befits a gentleman of noble birth such as myself?. The coat on me has been worn down badly due to my recent bad fortune, and I cannot let common soldiers mistake me as one of their own."), #Lothar
  ("npc10_payment", "That's good news. But I'll ask for one last thing, warlord. I have a woman here in {s20}, a tavern wench, and she says she has my child in her belly. Damn, she is a Brythonic wench, but I want to give her some money before I leave... for the child, you know. Even if the child's only half-Saxon, it still deserves some future. Do you think you can spare {reg3} scillingas?"), #Ceawlin
  ("npc11_payment", "Hey thank you {handsome/beauty}. But before joining up with you, I would like a payment of {reg3} scillingas. You know, as a token of our new relation."), #Gwenllian
  ("npc12_payment", "Before I sign up, i need pay 300 coins here."), #Orosio
  ("npc13_payment", "Ah, one last thing. I would like an initial bounty of {reg3} scillingas before I join your command. It's my principle never to enter someone's service without receiving the payment I deserve."), #Liuva
  ("npc14_payment", "Before I sign up, there is the small matter of some expenses I have incurred while staying here -- {reg3} scillingas. Do you think that you could cover those for me, as a gesture of our already legendary friendship?"), #Brian
  ("npc15_payment", "Good. By the way, as a skilled engineer I would expect a payment for my services. A signing bonus of {reg3} scillingas would be fair, I think."), #Agasicles
  ("npc16_payment", "Before I sign up, I will need 200 coins here."), #Aedh
  ("npc_bashe_payment", "Before I sign up, I will require 300 coins in payment."),
  ("npc_sange_payment", "Nice, but I need to pay 300 coins to the quastuosa before we go. I assume you can take care of that for me?"),
  ("npc_paintrain_payment", "My service doesn't come cheap, I'll need {reg3} scillingas."),
  ("npc_hammertime_payment", "I would be glad to pledge my fealty to you for {reg3} coins."),
  ("npc_tank_payment", "For the price of {reg3} scillingas, I would lend you my live."),
  ("npc_backwoodsharry_payment", "My service shall be yours, but I need {reg3} coins for a new shirt first."),
  ("npc_deadeye_payment", "I'll take your hand, Captain, and your aid.  Would you mind advancing me {reg3} scillingas? I also need to settle accounts with this establishment, and acquire certain necessaries."),
  ("npc_probulator_payment", "If you were to give me {reg3} scillingas, I would serve you."),
  ("npc_grim_payment", "Good! Good! Just one more thing before we leave.  Would you mind lending me {reg3} scillingas? It shames me to say it, but I have drunk more mead and wine this week past, than I have money left to pay."),
  ("npc_enchantress_payment", "I will support your for a donation of {reg3} scillingas."),

