  ("npc2_2ary_morality_speech", "{Sir/Madame} -- I'm not altogether happy that we {s21}. I'm a merchant, and in our business one is bounded by one's word. I don't want a reputation for dishonesty -- that would spell my end as a trader, {sir/madame}."),
  ("npc3_2ary_morality_speech", "{Sir/Madame} -- I think it was a brave decision you took to {s21}. There is no shame in finding a way to avoid the spilling of blood."),
