  ("npc5_2ary_morality_speech", "I think it was a brave decision you took to {s21}. There is no shame in finding a way to avoid the spilling of blood."),
  ("npc6_2ary_morality_speech", "{Sir/Madame} -- you may choose to {s21}, but I would prefer to have no part in it. Such is not the path to my redemption, nor does it help kill Visigoths."),
