  ("npc1_kingsupport_2b", "Well. We saw how that turned out, you drunk poor-sighted excuse of a tracker..."), #Osmund
  ("npc2_kingsupport_2b", "I do not ask for their support, as they would no doubt wish to make a profit on the transaction."), #Aleifr
  ("npc3_kingsupport_2b", "I have no intention of helping any more slaves, sorry."), #Eithne
  ("npc4_kingsupport_2b", "I don't have any, unfortunately."), #Athrwys
  ("npc5_kingsupport_2b", "No, I believe the lords should resolve their disputes by blood, and blood only. Laws are only useful to the weak."), #Frioc
  ("npc6_kingsupport_2b", "I am sorry, but my future kingdom will not meddle with continental affairs."), #Bodero
  ("npc7_kingsupport_2b", "Sorry, even though I respect you for your abilities, warriors, men, and Britons, are usually way more deserving than others."), #Bridei
  ("npc8_kingsupport_2b", "That's a pretty tall condition -- and after I am {king/queen}, I want nothing to do with the continent."), #Siwi.
  ("npc9_kingsupport_2b", "I'm not sure that implementing your idea would be as 'simple' as you think"), #Lothar
  ("npc10_kingsupport_2b", "You are out of your mind. There are valorous and noble men from every nation."), #Ceawlin
  ("npc11_kingsupport_2b", "I am no Arthur. Forget about it."), #Gwenllian
  ("npc12_kingsupport_2b", "Enough, sir. I will not have you mock our traditions."), #Orosio
  ("npc13_kingsupport_2b", "Actually, I was looking forward to a bit of rest after becoming king, and I don't want anything to do with the damn rest of Europe!"), #Liuva
  ("npc14_kingsupport_2b", "Hmm. I'm not sure about that. Cu Chulainn had a tragic and early death, I don't want to risk such a thing by comparing myself to him."), #Brian
  ("npc15_kingsupport_2b", "{King/Queen} of the weak and the poor, maybe. Enough of such talk."), #Agasicles
  ("npc16_kingsupport_2b", "No offense, but I'm not sure that's the approach I'd take -- you see, perhads Wotan or Thor, or even Macha would not like that at all."), #Aedh
