  ("npc_enchantress_kingsupport_objection", "I cannot agree with the arguments you allowed to be said in your name for the sake of your future as King. They are wrong, terribly wrong. And you know it. I am sorry to speak my mind in this rude tone, but I could no longer keep my mouth shut in face of such iniquity."), #klethi
  
