  ("npc1_turn_against", "I'm sorry that we meet like this, chief. There's no question that I owe my rise in life to you. You doubtless think me ungrateful. However, one has to follow one's destiny -- isn't that correct?"), #Osmund
  ("npc2_turn_against", "This is a sad day. I never thought that I might meet my old warlord on the field of battle. Even if I triumph, it will bring me no joy."), #Aleifr
  ("npc3_turn_against", "Oh {playername} -- what a tragic turn our lives have taken! I can only hope that the tides of war that have made us enemies, will one day allow us to be friends."), #Eithne
  ("npc4_turn_against", "Aye, well.... I'm not sure what to say. If we must fight, let's get it over with."), #Athrwys
  ("npc5_turn_against", "{playername}! It is a shame that we have to battle, after so many glorious victories we achieved together. Anyway, today I come against you with my sword raised. But I hope that one day we raise a glass together, to a friendship renewed."), #Frioc
  ("npc6_turn_against", "It grieves me more than anything I can say to meet you like this, {playername}. I shall not dwell on the circumstances that have led us to this point. I can only hope that we may one day be reconciled."), #Bodero
  ("npc7_turn_against", "Well, old leader. You made of me a great lady, and for that I am grateful. However, you did not buy me, and now the circumstances have caused our interests to clash, I can meet you in battle with a clear conscience. Still, I hope someday that circumstances may change again, and even though you will suffer defeat, we may meet as friends again."), #Bridei
  ("npc8_turn_against", "So, we meet now as enemies, and may shortly face each other over the rims of our shields. A grim day this is. Sometimes, the spinners of our fate have a dark sense of humor."), #Siwi
  ("npc9_turn_against", "I will not accept fault for the circumstances which have led us to become enemies. I want you to know that my conscience is clear, although my heart is heavy."), #Lothar
  ("npc10_turn_against", "Well, it looks like the tides of fate have led me to make war on my old dryhten. Maybe things started to go wrong when you became my liege -- I suppose I was never much suited to vassalage. Anyway, here we are now -- be ready to be defeated."), #Ceawlin
  ("npc11_turn_against", "Great Heaven, my heart is now as broken as shattered glass. So it looks like you and I are enemies. Didn't I say that life and love takes us on some very strange turns? Destiny sometimes has a cruel sense of humor -- to turn love into hate so easily."), #Gwenllian
  ("npc12_turn_against", "So, it seems we must fight. I would have you know, {sir/my lady}, that I have not betrayed you. I had never served you as a man, but served the principles which I believed you upheld. As you no longer uphold them, I must do my best to thwart you. But I bear you no ill will, and I hope that we can meet again someday as friends"), #Orosio
  ("npc13_turn_against", "Well, {playername}. We meet as enemies. I confess that I have mixed feelings. It grieves me to make war on you, but if we meet in battle and I prevail, I will have defeated the worthiest foe in all Britannia, and I will know that my mastery of the military art is complete!"), #Liuva
  ("npc14_turn_against", "It is sad to meet you as my enemy -- but on the other hand, to meet such a titan of the battlefield as yourself in combat is a rare privilege. Truly, the news of our contest today shall keep the bards and poets of Britannia in mead and silver for months to come, do you think?"), #Brian
  ("npc15_turn_against", "Ah... I have not been looking forward to this day. I just want to say that in my sight, if you'd kept your faith in me, things would never have come to this. But no doubt you see it differently."), #Agasicles
  ("npc16_turn_against", "I now see that for the time we travelled together you intended only to use and deceive me. For your soul belongs to the Devil, and the darkness of passion for the old gods lingers within your heart. For the peace of Christ, I must now defeat you in the field. Do not doubt that God is by my side today, and nothing but defeat is prepared for you right now."), #Aedh  
  ("npc_bashe_turn_against", "Hello, Warlord! So, I guess we're enemies! One small word of warning if we end up fighting each other -- once the rage of battle hits me, I can't always account for my actions. Just know that whatever I do, it's all because of the profound hate I now harbor against you. Maybe if we both walk away from this now, you will be able to spare you sorry life from my wrath."), 
  ("npc_sange_turn_against", "Hello, Warlord! So, I guess we're enemies! One small word of warning if we end up fighting each other -- once the rage of battle hits me, I can't always account for my actions. Just know that whatever I do, it's all because of the profound hate I now harbor against you. Maybe if we both walk away from this now, you will be able to spare you sorry life from my wrath."), 
  ("npc_paintrain_turn_against", "Hello, Captain! So, I guess we're enemies! One small word of warning if we end up fighting each other -- once the rage of battle hits me, I can't always account for my actions. Just know that whatever I do, it's not personal. Maybe if we both walk away from this, we can meet once more as friends?"), #klethi
  ("npc_hammertime_turn_against", "I had not expected that we would face each other on the field of battle one day, but don't expect me to go easy on you."), #klethi
  ("npc_tank_turn_against", "To think, that one day we would meet each other on the field of battle... Don't expect me to hold back."), #klethi
  ("npc_backwoodsharry_turn_against", "So we meet again, very well, I will have you taste my blade!"), #klethi
  ("npc_deadeye_turn_against", "So we are enemies now, I had not forseen this."), #klethi
  ("npc_probulator_turn_against", "So we are enemies now, I had not forseen this."), #klethi
  ("npc_grim_turn_against", "So we are enemies now, I had not forseen this."), #klethi
  ("npc_enchantress_turn_against", "Hello, Captain! So, I guess we're enemies! One small word of warning if we end up fighting each other -- once the rage of battle hits me, I can't always account for my actions. Just know that whatever I do, it's not personal. Maybe if we both walk away from this, we can meet once more as friends?"), #klethi

