	("spy_not_present","You have no spy in {s5}."),
	
	("spy_infiltrating", "Your spy is infiltrating {s5}."),
	
	("poison_well_desc"," My {Lord/Lady}, I have discovered a potent toxin that will disable a goodly number of the population.^If you so wish it, I could mix it into the well water at very little risk of discovery.^Though the toxin will be highly diluted in the well, it should still disable anyone drinking it for atleast a day, perhaps longer.^I will require 500 scillinga for expenses." ),
	
	("poison_cattle_desc"," My {Lord/Lady}, the wealth of a village is not measured in scillingas, but in cattle.^If the herd was unfortunate enough to be inflicted with some unknown pox, the villagers could not pay their taxes.^Thus, their lord would be financially weakened.^I imagine it would take a village weeks to recoupe such a devastating loss.^The cattle could acquire such a pox for a mere 500 scillingas."),
	
	("cause_unrest_desc"," My {Lord/Lady}, the local populace are a brutish lot.^A subtly whispered rumor here and there could stir old grudges into all out rioting.^I can think of nothing more devastating for production and the economy.^Send me 500 scillinga for expenses and I will cause such joyous chaos as this place has never seen!"),
	
	("poison_food_desc"," My {Lord/Lady}, after leaving the local drinking establishment, I happened to litterally stumble across a bit of useful information.^There before my eyes was a crack in the grainery.^With a bit of work, and 500 scillinga for expenses, I'm sure the crack could accomodate all sizes of vermin into the food stocks.^The troops would have naught but rats to eat during an extended siege."),
	
